thoonga nagaram ( tamil : தூங்கா நகரம் ; english : the city never sleeps ) is a 2011 indian tamil-language drama-thriller film written and directed by debutant gaurav narayanan , starring himself along with vimal , bharani , nishanth and anjali in the lead roles .   the film , produced by dhayanidhi alagiri 's cloud nine movies , was shot entirely in madurai , the city where the story takes place and which the title refers to .   it was released on 4 february 2011 to relatively positive reviews and excellent box office collection .